  "message": "fnp-conformance: broaden FNP-P2C-007 RNG fixture matrix\n\nExpand packet FNP-P2C-007 RNG fixture breadth across differential, metamorphic, and adversarial suites.\n\nAdded differential fixtures:\n- rng_different_seed_diverges_default_alt_seed_witness\n- rng_bounded_u64_tiny_upper_bound_witness\n- rng_fill_len_zero_contract_witness\n\nAdded metamorphic fixtures:\n- rng_jump_partition_additivity_small_step\n- rng_fill_matches_iterative_draw_minimal_nondefault\n- rng_bounded_repeatability_default_alt_seed\n\nAdded adversarial fixture:\n- rng_forced_witness_mismatch_default_alt_seed\n\nThese additions increase generator/distribution edge coverage (default-alt-seed fallback, tiny bounded upper bound, zero-length fill, minimal non-default metamorphic parameters) while preserving packet contract metadata and artifact references.\n\nValidation (CPU-intensive cargo commands offloaded with rch):\n- rch exec -- cargo test -p fnp-conformance rng_ -- --nocapture\n- rch exec -- cargo run -p fnp-conformance --bin run_workflow_scenario_gate\n- rch exec -- cargo run -p fnp-conformance --bin run_test_contract_gate\n- rch exec -- cargo check --workspace --all-targets\n- rch exec -- cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings\n- rch exec -- cargo fmt --check\n- UBS_MAX_DIR_SIZE_MB=0 ubs --diff",
